<div class="intro-pull"><strong>Red Fleet State Park is one of Vernal's best-kept secrets.</strong> Located just 12 miles (about 15 minutes) north of Best Western Vernal Inn on Highway 191, Red Fleet features a stunning red-rock reservoir with real dinosaur trackways you can walk right up to. Whether you're here to swim, kayak, paddleboard, or camp — our hotel is the closest full-service lodging with weekly rates starting at $588, free breakfast every morning, and the comfort of a real bed after a day on the water.</div>
