<p>Red Fleet State Park doesn't have lodges or cabins — it's a day-use and camping park. Guests who want hot showers, a real breakfast, and a comfortable room choose Best Western Vernal Inn as their base. At just 12 miles (15 minutes) north of the hotel, you can be at the reservoir before most campers wake up. Rates start at $84/night, or $588 for a full week.</p>
