<div class="pro-tip"><p><strong>Pro Tip:</strong> The dinosaur trackway trail is about a 1.5-mile round trip from the parking area. Go in the morning when the light hits the tracks at an angle — they're much easier to see. Then head back to the hotel (15 minutes) for breakfast.</p></div>
